article.description: — DeVante' Jones had 25 points as Coastal Carolina easily defeated Greensboro 103-45 on Saturday.
article.headline: Jones carries Coastal Carolina over Greensboro 103-45
article.linkText: Jones carries Coastal Carolina over Greensboro 103-45
article.story: CONWAY, S.C. -- — DeVante' Jones had 25 points as Coastal Carolina easily defeated Greensboro 103-45 on Saturday. Essam Mostafa had 12 points and nine rebounds for Coastal Carolina (4-0). Ahmard Harvey added 10 points, and DeShawn Thomas had nine rebounds and four blocks. Matthew Brown had 10 points for the Pride. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
